{
  "texts": [
    "We performed pretraining using a masked language modelling objective (cf. https://tinyurl.",
    "com/5n8bjnbh).",
    "For hyperparameters and further training details see Suppl.",
    "Section S3.",
    "In many safety-critical domains, in particular in the clinical domain, it is crucial to (1) understand the inner workings of a model (faithfulness) and to (2) evaluate how convincing a model interpretation is for a human observer (plausibility) (Jacovi and Goldberg 2020)."
  ]
